    <span>Causal Learner is an easy-to-use open source toolbox for causal structure and Markov blanket (MB) learning. The relationship between global causal structure, 
        local causal structure, and MB is shown in Figure 1 (T is a target node in black).<br/><br/>
        Causal Learner provides discrete data and continuous data generating functions, causal structure learning and MB learning algorithms, and algorithm evaluation functions.
        The data generation part of Causal Learner is written in R language, and the rest of Causal Learner is written in MATLAB. Causal Learner is is an open-source version of the will-known causality learning toolbox Causal Explorer, which makes research efforts on causal structure learning and MB learning much easier.<br/>
    </span>
      
